1 - After npx create-react-app ProjectName

2 - Installed some dependencies:
        - npm install react-router-dom
        - npm install gsap (This is the greensock animation library)
        - npm styled-components (lets you add the css style in the same js folder my setting variables for the tag names)

        E.G (styled components):
  
          Regular HTML
            <div>
                <img src='' alt=''/>
            </div>
          
          HTML with styled components

            <Container>
                <Image src='' alt=''/>
            </Container>

            const Container = styled.div`
            Here you add the css code :)
            `;

            const Image = styled.img``;

3 - Delete all the code in app.css to add:

        * {
    margin: 0;
        }

4 - I created Animation Component to import to App.js

5 - In the StartAnimation.js I added the Container (<div></div>) and inside
    I placed the svg code in the StartAnimation component.